### Empty cart — joins /internal/cart with /internal/products.
GET http://localhost:3003/api/cart

### Add an item — handler updates /internal/products stock + inserts into /internal/cart.
POST http://localhost:3003/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json

{ "product_id": 1, "quantity": 2 }

### Cart now has the item with name + subtotal joined in.
GET http://localhost:3003/api/cart

### Out-of-stock guard.
POST http://localhost:3003/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json

{ "product_id": 3, "quantity": 999 }
